<ul>
    <li>Basic identification details (name, student ID, contact information)</li>
    <li>Academic information</li>
    <li>Appointment scheduling preferences</li>
    <li>Counselling session notes (stored securely and confidentially)</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>Your information is used solely for:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Providing effective counselling services</li>
